This paper deals with the problem of finding frequently co-occurring items in a database, which is a common problem in data structures (cs.DS) and databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the use of sketches, which is a common technique in information theory (cs.IT) and computational complexity (cs.CC). Finally, the problem of finding frequent itemsets is a well-studied topic in data mining (cs.DM).
